<paragraph blockId="4.[170,795,1552,1936]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[170,297,1552,1577]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Type data:</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus box="[356,457,1552,1577]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schrottky" authorityYear="1913" box="[498,793,1552,1577]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Hemisia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="variety" species="garleppi" variety="unifasciata">
<emphasis box="[498,616,1552,1577]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">C. garleppi</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[673,793,1552,1577]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">unifasciata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was also collected by Otto Garlepp in the same locality that 
<emphasis box="[222,343,1617,1642]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schrottky" authorityYear="1913" box="[222,340,1617,1642]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Hemisia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="garleppi">C. garleppi</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus box="[395,496,1617,1642]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">holotype</typeStatus>
is housed at 
<collectionCode box="[643,707,1617,1642]" country="Brazil" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/5xp9-edpx" name="Universidade Federal do Parana, Colecao de Entomologia Pe. Jesus Santiago Moure" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="University or college">DZUP</collectionCode>
