<bibRefCitation author="Moure, J. S." box="[291,439,1650,1675]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refId="ref4466" refString="Moure, J. S. 1999 [2000]. Algumas especies de Centris (Paracentris) (Hymenoptera, Anthophoridae). Acta BiolOgica Paranaense, 28 (1,2,3,4): 147 - 158. DOI" type="book" year="1999">Moure (1999)</bibRefCitation>
it also belongs to the 
<collectionCode box="[682,745,1650,1675]" country="Brazil" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/9yp6-zxp9" name="Sao Paulo, Museu de Zoologia da Universidade de Sao Paulo" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="Museum">MZSP</collectionCode>
.The specimen has the following data label: 
